| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6892 — Recovery Inhibition (babuk2)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e50ad8f6-4f03-59dd-b624-6fe10015dd2c"
